<br>
On the other hand, I don't believe in the death penalty under any circumstances.  Try them in a military tribunal if you want, it's fine with me, but don't execute them.<br>
<br>
Ammelen <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/bvazaellecommunitycenter.showUserPublicProfile?gid=truthreason>TruthReason</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>I'm actually Goanad.</span><br>  Posts: 1254<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/27/03 12:42 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=72.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Yay, an American Death Camp</span><hr size=1> IT would be horrible to see executions take place. However, tribunals are in place to deal with these individuals. These tribunals are appropriate for those classified as &quot;combatants&quot; against the US. <br>
<br>
They are not American citizens any more than Adolph Eichman was. Did Eichman deserve a day in Federal Court?  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/bvazaellecommunitycenter.showUserPublicProfile?gid=herdervazaelle>HerderVazaelle</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>I Live Here</span><br>  Posts: 2160<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/27/03 1:24 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=72.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> And so...</span><hr size=1> So, what you are saying is that &quot;foreigners&quot; don't deserve the same kind of justice that americans are granted.<br>
